<h2 class="bold font-l">Magic User's Club</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Next time, Sae, go BEFORE you get stuck in a closet with some dude! </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PottyEmergency" class='trope-example-link'>Potty Emergency</a></p>
</div>
